## 🚀 **Live Demo**
🔗 **DocAI is deployed on Vercel**:  
👉 **[https://doc-ai.vercel.app](https://doc-ai.vercel.app)**

---

## 🛠 **Tech Stack**
- **Backend**: Python, AWS Lambda, Boto3, Anthropic Claude AI, OpenAI  
- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript  
- **Database**: PostgreSQL  
- **Auth**: JWT (JSON Web Tokens)  
- **Deployment**: Vercel  

---

